text: AKM Khalequzzaman is a Bangladesh Muslim League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Kishoreganj-6. ==Career== Khalequzzaman was elected to parliament from Kishoreganj-6 as a Bangladesh Muslim League candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Muslim League politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: AKM Khalequzzaman
